    "Ultimately, the findings of this study have practical implications for investors, financial institutions, and policymakers pursuing sustainable and profitable investment strategies.",
    "However, the study still has certain limitations.",
    "First, the unstructured data used in this study are all text, and in the era of big data, images and videos should also be taken into account in the future.",
    "Second, as this study has yielded these outstanding findings while focusing on emerging economic markets, the effectiveness of the proposed approach should be evaluated further in other markets.",
    "Third, the volatility of financial markets related with stocks (e.g., gold, crude oil) may also play a role in stock price volatility and these should be incorporated effectively into the features."
